comment: mvc-showcase update for 3.1 and latest jquery
updated README to provide more links for new users
Simplified dependencies; updated artifact name to spring-mvc-showcase for consistency
Add examples of mapping by consumes/produces conditions.
Add '@PathVariables available in the model when rendering' and 'Data binding with URI variables' under the Views tab
Add example of annotating method argument with @Valid @RequestBody. Switch to using @ModelAttribute for application/x-www-form-urlencoded data (instead of MultiValueMap).
Add links on 'Writing Responses' tab with response containing UTF-8 characters.
Improve back button behavior on tabs with redirect or full page reload.
